text:
Thanks for the housewarming card.

Now that the house is warmed,
can I still keep the present
you sent with it?

Thanks for the housewarming card!
I loved it AND the gift!

I wanted to give you something too
so there's a thing attached!

It was so nice of you to send
me that housewarming gift,
n\0! Lemme warm
your house up now!

Your housewarming card made me
happy! I'm unpacking my stuff. I've
got crates of snacks, bugs to put in
the floors, and I gotta figure out
how to put my bed together...but
your card makes it all easier!

I was so nervous when I first moved
here... But your note helped me
relax! Thanks, n\0!
You should come chill at my place
sometime. I have snacks!

You sent me a letter and that was
cool! I just got here, and I don't
even know my own address, so I
dunno how you figured it out!
